text: Ivona Svobodnikova (born 1 April 1991) is a Czech volleyball player. She played at the 2011 Women's European Volleyball League, 2013 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, and 2016 FIVB World Grand Prix. She played for Post-Telekom-Sportverein Aachen. == References == Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Czech volleyball players
